<h2 id="toc0"><span>Essophysics</span></h2>
<div style="margin-left: 20px">
<p>Essophysics is the study of embodiments. It is the discovery of everyday gods — usually hidden, always watching. Reality bends to their will, but they are all flawed. None know the heights and depths of human experience, none are all-powerful, all are subject to the discordancy of conceptualization. All are mortal. Painfully, obviously mortal.</p>
</div>
