<h2 id="toc1"><span>AMEC and DRO</span></h2>
<div style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px">
<p>The Anti-Memetic Entities Catalog (AMEC) operates as a classified twin to the standard SCiPNET database, using specialized memetic inoculation to bypass the antimemetic effects of certain anomalous objects. These objects are given an Item Number of DRO-####, standing for Documentation-Resistant Object.</p>
</div>
