<h2 id="toc2"><span>Timeline Of Important Events</span></h2>
<div style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px">
<p>This primarily exists as a vain attempt to ensure that characters born in 1990 don't become Site Directors in 1970. It's harder than you'd think!</p>
